ent is somehow exceeding it.\n\n2. **review**: 2 tasks, avg 24 steps, successRat
e=1 but 3 errors (100% error rate). The review error rate is reported as 100% be
cause ALL review tasks hit errors.\n\n3. **e2e**: 2 tasks, avg 10 steps, success
